name: MSRI-QUADRO-GIFGBIV-01
description: This is gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Green, Blue, Indigo, Violet. The 4 views are the 4 cameras of the same object in different scale in 512*512 pixels [upper left is for "top" view; down left is for "front" view, down right is for "right" view and upper right is for "custom perspective"]. Total 64 frames, 1024*1024 px square.
